<li>Suppose you are given that <m>I_T(92,80) = 3.75</m> and <m>I_H(92,80) = 0.8</m>.  Estimate the values of <m>I(91,80)</m> and <m>I(92,78)</m>.  Explain how the partial derivatives are relevant to your thinking.</li>
